  "remarks": "\n Irek Envarovich FAIZULLIN, is a prominent Russian politician. FAIZULLIN is, or has been, involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia as a member of the Board of Directors of the state-owned Russian Railways which is an entity carrying on business in the transport sector - a sector of strategic importance to the Government of Russia. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
